From: "Ronnie Feitelson" <Ronnie(-at-)OldVolks.com>

> Call Rancho Trans  714  680 6737 ask them to sell you a 68/69 bus
> bellhousing. Then get yourself a 12 volt to 6 volt bushing to be able to use
> a 6 volt starter. You can then buy a cheap engine stand (Harbour Freight)
> and bolt the bellhousing to it. Easy cheap way to do it.
